{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":744,"text":"When I was about 16 years old"},{"time":3742,"text":"I can remember flipping through channels at home during summer vacation,"},{"time":7441,"text":"looking for a movie to watch on HBO --"},{"time":9971,"text":"and how many of you remember \"Ferris Bueller's Day Off\"?"},{"time":12484,"text":"Oh yeah, great movie, right? -- Well, I saw Matthew Broderick on the screen, and so I thought,"},{"time":17485,"text":"\"Sweet! Ferris Bueller. I'll watch this!\""},{"time":20197,"text":"It wasn't Ferris Bueller. And forgive me Matthew Broderick,"},{"time":23769,"text":"I know you've done other movies besides Ferris Bueller, but that's how I remember you; you're Ferris."},{"time":27886,"text":"But you weren't doing Ferris-y things at the time; you were doing gay things at the time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":33639,"text":"He was in a movie called \"Torch Song Trilogy.\""},{"time":36967,"text":"And \"Torch Song Trilogy\" was based on a play about this drag queen who essentially was looking for love."},{"time":43713,"text":"Love and respect -- that's what the whole film was about."}]},{"cues":[{"time":46777,"text":"And as I'm watching it, I'm realizing that they're talking about me."},{"time":51933,"text":"Not the drag queen part -- I am not shaving my hair for anyone -- but the gay part."},{"time":57526,"text":"The finding love and respect, the part about trying to find your place in the world."},{"time":62739,"text":"So as I'm watching this, I see this powerful scene that brought me to tears,"},{"time":69089,"text":"and it stuck with me for the past 25 years."},{"time":72289,"text":"And there's this quote that the main character, Arnold, tells his mother"},{"time":77398,"text":"as they're fighting about who he is and the life that he lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":82557,"text":"\"There's one thing more -- there's just one more thing you better understand."},{"time":87776,"text":"I've taught myself to sew, cook, fix plumbing, build furniture,"},{"time":93812,"text":"I can even pat myself on the back when necessary,"},{"time":96669,"text":"all so I don't have to ask anyone for anything."},{"time":101168,"text":"There's nothing I need from anyone except for love and respect,"},{"time":106847,"text":"and anyone who can't give me those two things has no place in my life.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":111296,"text":"I remember that scene like it was yesterday; I was 16, I was in tears, I was in the closet,"},{"time":119063,"text":"and I'm looking at these two people, Ferris Bueller and some guy I'd never seen before,"},{"time":124424,"text":"fighting for love."},{"time":128722,"text":"When I finally got to a place in my life"},{"time":132851,"text":"where I came out and accepted who I was, and was really quite happy, to tell you the truth,"},{"time":136474,"text":"I was happily gay and I guess that's supposed to be right because gay means happy too."},{"time":140620,"text":"I realized there were a lot of people who weren't as gay as I was --"},{"time":144949,"text":"gay being happy, not gay being attracted to the same sex."},{"time":148167,"text":"In fact, I heard that there was a lot of hate and a lot of anger"},{"time":153211,"text":"and a lot of frustration and a lot of fear\n"},{"time":155821,"text":"about who I was and the gay lifestyle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":160690,"text":"Now, I'm sitting here trying to figure out \"the gay lifestyle,\" \"the gay lifestyle,\""},{"time":165011,"text":"and I keep hearing this word over and over and over again: lifestyle, lifestyle, lifestyle."},{"time":169423,"text":"I've even heard politicians say that the gay lifestyle is a greater threat"},{"time":174053,"text":"to civilization than terrorism."},{"time":176961,"text":"That's when I got scared."},{"time":179936,"text":"Because I'm thinking, if I'm gay and I'm doing something that's going to destroy civilization,"},{"time":187058,"text":"I need to figure out what this stuff is, and I need to stop doing it right now."},{"time":191684,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":194062,"text":"So, I took a look at my life, a hard look at my life,"},{"time":198985,"text":"and I saw some things very disturbing."},{"time":203205,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":207041,"text":"And I want to begin sharing these evil things that I've been doing with you,"},{"time":210795,"text":"starting with my mornings."},{"time":213092,"text":"I drink coffee."},{"time":216138,"text":"Not only do I drink coffee, I know other gay people who drink coffee."},{"time":222031,"text":"I get stuck in traffic --"},{"time":225673,"text":"evil, evil traffic."},{"time":229151,"text":"Sometimes I get stuck in lines at airports."}]},{"cues":[{"time":232323,"text":"I look around, and I go, \"My God, look at all these gay people!"},{"time":235589,"text":"We're all trapped in these lines! These long lines trying to get on an airplane!"},{"time":240031,"text":"My God, this lifestyle that I'm living is so freaking evil!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":246257,"text":"I clean up. This is not an actual photograph of my son's room; his is messier."},{"time":253644,"text":"And because I have a 15-year-old, all I do is cook and cook and cook."},{"time":259021,"text":"Any parents out there of teenagers? All we do is cook for these people --"},{"time":263962,"text":"they eat two, three, four dinners a night -- it's ridiculous!"},{"time":268766,"text":"This is the gay lifestyle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":271414,"text":"And after I'm done cooking and cleaning and standing in line and getting stuck in traffic,"},{"time":278201,"text":"my partner and I, we get together"},{"time":281804,"text":"and we decide that we're gonna go and have some wild and crazy fun."},{"time":287959,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":291783,"text":"We're usually in bed before we find out who's eliminated on \"American Idol.\""},{"time":295135,"text":"We have to wake up and find out the next day who's still on"},{"time":299353,"text":"because we're too freaking tired to hear who stays on."},{"time":304439,"text":"This is the super duper evil gay lifestyle."},{"time":308809,"text":"Run for your heterosexual lives, people."},{"time":312674,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":321068,"text":"When my partner, Steve, and I first started dating,"},{"time":325722,"text":"he told me this story about penguins."},{"time":329316,"text":"And I didn't know where he was going with it at first."},{"time":332767,"text":"He was kind of a little bit nervous when he was sharing it with me, but he told me that"},{"time":336703,"text":"when a penguin finds a mate that they want to spend the rest of their life with,"},{"time":341056,"text":"they present them with a pebble -- the perfect pebble."},{"time":344657,"text":"And then he reaches into his pocket, and he brings this out to me."},{"time":351273,"text":"And I looked at it, and I was like, this is really cool."}]},{"cues":[{"time":355250,"text":"And he says, \"I want to spend the rest of my life with you.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":359676,"text":"So I wear this whenever I have to do something that makes me a little nervous,"},{"time":365215,"text":"like, I don't know, a TEDx talk."},{"time":368804,"text":"I wear this when I am apart from him for a long period of time."},{"time":372790,"text":"And sometimes I just wear it just because."}]},{"cues":[{"time":376410,"text":"How many people out there are in love? Anyone in love out there?"},{"time":381328,"text":"You might be gay."},{"time":384504,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":385930,"text":"Because I, too, am in love, and apparently that's part of the gay lifestyle that I warned you about."},{"time":392479,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":398744,"text":"You may want to tell your spouse. Who, if they're in love, might be gay as well."},{"time":404316,"text":"How many of you are single? Any single people out there?"},{"time":408218,"text":"You too might be gay! Because I know some gay people who are also single."},{"time":413384,"text":"It's really scary, this gay lifestyle thing; it's super duper evil and there's no end to it!"},{"time":420129,"text":"It goes and goes and engulfs!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":423473,"text":"It's really quite silly, isn't it?"},{"time":426329,"text":"That's why I'm so happy to finally hear President Obama come out and say"},{"time":431718,"text":"\n(Applause)"},{"time":433713,"text":"that he supports --"},{"time":435775,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":439198,"text":"that he supports marriage equality."},{"time":442560,"text":"It's a wonderful day in our country's history; it's a wonderful day in the globe's history"},{"time":447130,"text":"to be able to have an actual sitting president say, enough of this --"},{"time":452176,"text":"first to himself, and then to the rest of the world."},{"time":455890,"text":"It's wonderful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":457978,"text":"But there's something that's been disturbing me since he"},{"time":461369,"text":"made that remark just a short time ago."},{"time":465106,"text":"And that is, apparently, this is just another move by the gay activists"},{"time":471666,"text":"that's on the gay agenda."},{"time":475147,"text":"And I'm disturbed by this because I've been openly gay now for quite some time."},{"time":480860,"text":"I've been to all of the functions, I've been to fundraisers,"},{"time":484550,"text":"I've written about the topic, and I have yet to receive my copy of this gay agenda."},{"time":489035,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":490725,"text":"I've paid my dues on time,"},{"time":493507,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":496056,"text":"I've marched in gay pride flags parades and the whole nine,"},{"time":500351,"text":"and I've yet to see a copy of the gay agenda.\n"},{"time":503692,"text":"It's very, very frustrating, and I was feeling left out, like I wasn't quite gay enough."}]},{"cues":[{"time":508657,"text":"But then something wonderful happened: I was out shopping, as I tend to do,"},{"time":513860,"text":"and I came across a bootleg copy of the official gay agenda."}]},{"cues":[{"time":522283,"text":"And I said to myself, \"LZ, for so long, you have been denied this."},{"time":527687,"text":"When you get in front of this crowd, you're gonna share the news."},{"time":532703,"text":"You're gonna spread the gay agenda so no one else has to wonder,"},{"time":536574,"text":"what exactly is in the gay agenda?"},{"time":540095,"text":"What are these gays up to?"},{"time":543575,"text":"What do they want?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":546409,"text":"So, without further ado, I will present to you, ladies and gentlemen --"},{"time":551796,"text":"now be careful, 'cause it's evil -- a copy,"},{"time":556030,"text":"the official copy, of the gay agenda."},{"time":561463,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":586267,"text":"The gay agenda, people!"},{"time":589238,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":593175,"text":"There it is!"},{"time":595227,"text":"Did you soak it all in? The gay agenda."}]},{"cues":[{"time":599066,"text":"Some of you may be calling it, what,"},{"time":602317,"text":"the Constitution of the United States, is that what you call it too?"},{"time":605461,"text":"The U.S. Constitution is the gay agenda."},{"time":610661,"text":"These gays, people like me, want to be treated like full citizens"},{"time":615566,"text":"and it's all written down in plain sight."},{"time":619471,"text":"I was blown away when I saw it. I was like, wait, this is the gay agenda?"},{"time":625177,"text":"Why didn't you just call it the Constitution so I knew what you were talking about?"},{"time":629386,"text":"I wouldn't have been so confused; I wouldn't have been so upset."},{"time":633074,"text":"But there it is. The gay agenda."},{"time":637782,"text":"Run for your heterosexual lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":643586,"text":"Did you know that in all the states where there is no shading that"},{"time":650318,"text":"people who are gay, lesbian, bisexual or transgendered"},{"time":653459,"text":"can be kicked out of their apartments"},{"time":655551,"text":"for being gay, lesbian, bisexual or transgendered?"},{"time":659687,"text":"That's the only reason that a landlord needs to have them removed,"},{"time":664855,"text":"because there's no protection from discrimination of GLBT people."},{"time":670697,"text":"Did you know in the states where there's no shading that"},{"time":675846,"text":"you can be fired for being gay, lesbian, bisexual or transgendered?"},{"time":682032,"text":"Not based upon the quality of your work,"},{"time":686043,"text":"how long you've been there, if you stink,"},{"time":690045,"text":"just if you're gay, lesbian, bisexual or transgendered."},{"time":696718,"text":"All of which flies in the face of the gay agenda,"},{"time":702048,"text":"also known as the U.S. Constitution."},{"time":705763,"text":"Specifically, this little amendment right here:"}]},{"cues":[{"time":709435,"text":"\"No state shall make or enforce any law which shall abridge the privileges or immunities"},{"time":714686,"text":"of citizens of the United States.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":718924,"text":"I'm looking at you, North Carolina."},{"time":721965,"text":"But you're not looking at the U.S. Constitution."},{"time":726562,"text":"This is the gay agenda: equality. Not special rights,"},{"time":731873,"text":"but the rights that were already written by these people --"},{"time":736049,"text":"these elitists, if you will."},{"time":738468,"text":"Educated, well-dressed,"},{"time":742499,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":745187,"text":"some would dare say questionably dressed."},{"time":747928,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":750707,"text":"Nonetheless, our forefathers, right?"},{"time":754489,"text":"The people that, we say, knew what they were doing when they wrote the Constitution --"},{"time":758725,"text":"the gay agenda, if you will."},{"time":761898,"text":"All of that flies in the face of what they did."}]},{"cues":[{"time":767221,"text":"That is the reason why I felt it was imperative that"},{"time":772732,"text":"I presented you with this copy of the gay agenda."},{"time":778074,"text":"Because I figured if I made it funny, you wouldn't be as threatened."},{"time":783052,"text":"I figured if I was a bit irreverent, you wouldn't find it serious."},{"time":787611,"text":"But when you see the map, and you see our state of Michigan --"},{"time":793038,"text":"it's legal to fire someone"},{"time":798685,"text":"for being gay, lesbian, bisexual or transgendered,"},{"time":802579,"text":"that it's legal to remove someone from their home"},{"time":806843,"text":"because they're gay, lesbian, bisexual or transgendered,"},{"time":811453,"text":"then you realize that this whole conversation about marriage equality"},{"time":815441,"text":"is not about stripping someone's rights away,"},{"time":818909,"text":"it's about granting them the rights that [have] already been stated."},{"time":823489,"text":"And we're just trying to walk in those rights that have already been stated,"},{"time":827950,"text":"that we've already agreed upon."},{"time":831456,"text":"There are people living in fear"},{"time":836763,"text":"of losing their jobs"},{"time":840380,"text":"so they don't show anyone who they really are"},{"time":845470,"text":"right here at home. This isn't just about North Carolina;"},{"time":850275,"text":"all those states that were clear, it's legal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":855964,"text":"If I could brag for a second,"},{"time":859188,"text":"I have a 15-year-old son from my marriage."},{"time":865292,"text":"He has a 4.0.\n"},{"time":868043,"text":"He is starting a new club at school, Policy Debate."},{"time":874482,"text":"He's a budding track star;"},{"time":878709,"text":"he has almost every single record in middle school for every event that he competed in."},{"time":885170,"text":"He volunteers."},{"time":887673,"text":"He prays before he eats."},{"time":890908,"text":"I would like to think, as his father -- and he lives with me primarily --"},{"time":897103,"text":"that I had a little something to do with all of that."},{"time":901020,"text":"I would like to think that he's a good boy,"},{"time":903928,"text":"a respectful young man. I would like to think that"},{"time":908295,"text":"I've proven to be a capable father."},{"time":911992,"text":"But if I were to go to the state of Michigan today,"},{"time":915745,"text":"and try to adopt a young person who is in an orphanage,"},{"time":920677,"text":"I would be disqualified for only one reason:"},{"time":924276,"text":"because I'm gay."},{"time":927633,"text":"It doesn't matter what I've already proven, what I can do with my heart."},{"time":932436,"text":"It's because of what the state of Michigan says that I am"},{"time":936044,"text":"that I am disqualified for any sort of adoption."},{"time":941876,"text":"And that's not just about me,"},{"time":945911,"text":"that's about so many other Michiganders, U.S. citizens,"},{"time":950814,"text":"who don't understand why what they are"},{"time":955973,"text":"is so much more significant than who they are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":961253,"text":"This story just keeps playing over and over"},{"time":966630,"text":"and over again in our country's history."},{"time":970121,"text":"There was a time in which, I don't know,"},{"time":973978,"text":"people who were black couldn't have the same rights."},{"time":978007,"text":"People who happened to be women didn't have the same rights, couldn't vote."},{"time":983322,"text":"There was a point in our history in which, if you were considered disabled,"},{"time":988112,"text":"that an employer could just fire you, before the Americans with Disabilities Act."},{"time":992849,"text":"We keep doing this over and over again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":996203,"text":"And so here we are, 2012,"},{"time":1000787,"text":"gay agenda,"},{"time":1003116,"text":"gay lifestyle, and I'm not a good dad"},{"time":1006984,"text":"and people don't deserve to be able to protect their families"},{"time":1010494,"text":"because of what they are, not who they are."},{"time":1015165,"text":"So when you hear the words \"gay lifestyle\" and \"gay agenda\" in the future,"},{"time":1021809,"text":"I encourage you to do two things:"},{"time":1025214,"text":"One, remember the U.S. Constitution, and then two,"},{"time":1031499,"text":"if you wouldn't mind looking to your left, please."},{"time":1036622,"text":"Look to your right."},{"time":1039778,"text":"That person next to you is a brother, is a sister."},{"time":1045245,"text":"And they should be treated with love and respect."},{"time":1047860,"text":"Thank you."}]}]}